      <title>抵押贷款利率下降，Toll 认为豪宅需求强劲</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/toll-sees-solid-demand-for-luxury-homes-as-mortgage-rates-fall</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于较低的抵押贷款利率引发了对该公司豪宅的需求，Toll Brothers Inc. 上调了全年财年的利润率预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/toll-sees-solid-demand-for-luxury-homes-as-mortgage-rates-fall</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 20:53:51 GMT</pubDate>
