      <title>加纳放弃对可可的外国资助，打破了 32 年的传统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/ghana-breaks-foreign-funding-of-cocoa-tradition-after-32-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加纳放弃了从国际银行借款来为下一季可可作物提供资金的计划，打破了 32 年来发展其农场和经济的传统。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/ghana-breaks-foreign-funding-of-cocoa-tradition-after-32-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 20:50:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美元连跌推动欧元、英镑创 2024 年新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/dollar-s-losing-streak-sends-euro-pound-to-fresh-2024-highs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美元的下跌刺激了其他主要货币的上涨，推动欧元和英镑创下 2024 年新高，因为交易员们开始关注未来的全球利率走势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/dollar-s-losing-streak-sends-euro-pound-to-fresh-2024-highs</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 16:50:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>克罗格出售 105 亿美元债券，为收购 Albertsons 提供资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/kroger-kicks-off-dollar-bond-sale-to-fund-albertsons-tie-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[克罗格公司周二出售了价值 105 亿美元的债券，为收购另一家食品杂货商 Albertsons Cos 提供资金，这是今年最大的公司债券交易之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/kroger-kicks-off-dollar-bond-sale-to-fund-albertsons-tie-up</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 12:24:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
